Package com.amazon.clouddrive.configuration

Configuration structures that are used with AmazonCloudDrive

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    EndpointsCache
    Defines a cache for holding the meta-data and content endpoints used for making requests to Amazon Cloud Drive.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AccountConfiguration
    Configuration that is specific to the customer's account.
    ClientConfiguration
    Defines configuration options for making requests to Amazon Cloud Drive.
    Endpoints
    A container class for holding a meta-data endpoint and a content endpoint.
    SimpleEndpointsCache
    A simple expiring endpoint cache.
